commit.title: [gitlab] Update to bionic.
commit.message:
[gitlab] Update to bionic.

We install all the based dependencies using APT, this will save us
some time in the future if we decide to build a custom docker image.

We also improve the coqide dependencies a bit, and manually version
the key cache. This is not perfect but should allow us to bump the
version when we modify `.gitlab-ci.yml` and avoid thus all the caching
problems.
